item.title: CVE-2015-10002|2024-08-06T08:58:24.563Z -- kiddoware -- kids%20place
item.description: A vulnerability classified as problematic has been found in Kiddoware Kids Place. This affects the Home Button Protection. A repeated pressing of the button causes a local denial of service. It is recommended to upgrade the affected component.
